{"tid":1227039,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啊啊啊啊啊啊！點解要做傻事阿！","createTime":"2019-06-15T14:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T15:03:47.000Z","uid":143343,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"423a457a4c2aa6635269391b01d7353cfb492bd8","tid":1227039,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:21:42.000Z","msg":"我個心好痛 明明就快迫到林鄭下台<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今晚我諗全香港人都訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好辛苦"},{"pid":"ff607e12d00c60b97c2f6915f73b3a2fd3505002","tid":1227039,"uid":143343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人同我一樣接受唔到喊左"},{"pid":"6172f18d9f9e794bd56c11622d2b91d94547365c","tid":1227039,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2df4a53fa58c679d075ee2eae92aa314fd6d27","tid":1227039,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24d580c118d8b8f9bd846dafdf5dce3388aa6b2","tid":1227039,"uid":39013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:24:32.000Z","msg":"呢排的心理壓力對於有良知的人黎講真係好大<br />\n其他巴絲都係有事要尋求幫助<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7e94c50f19b12b027256f01f5d73f17ca9dfd6","tid":1227039,"uid":123050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:25:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>行政機關濫用權力之審判</strong></span><br />\n二戰末期，納粹德國敗局已現，佛斯曼醫師、門格勒、拉舍爾三人的命運也隨著戰爭快速流轉。1945年時，拉舍爾因犯罪而被處死，和被他殺死的許多人一樣，葬身於達豪集中營裡。而門格勒假扮成一般士兵，躲過追緝後流亡到南美洲，直到1979年在巴西意外溺斃後才被確認身分。而始終堅持人性的佛斯曼醫師則在戰火中存活了下來，1945年時游過易北河後向美軍投降，戰後以泌尿科醫師的身份默默地生活著。在惡魔的年代結束之際，三名醫師分別擁來了他們各自的結局&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpansci.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg&h=327c7f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左上圖：將人浸入冰水當中，藉此研究在低溫下人體的反應；左下圖：故意讓小孩感染結核菌，並切除腋下的淋巴腺，測試人體的免疫力；右圖：紐倫堡審判中，對卡爾&middot;勃蘭特（Karl Brandt）醫師的審判，他被控同意並參與非人道實驗和其他戰爭罪行，最後被判絞刑。<br />\n用屍體換來的規範－紐倫堡守則<br />\n堆積如山的屍體、骨瘦如柴的幸存者，那些泯滅人性的實驗震撼了全世界。1948年在紐倫堡進行的醫師審判，被告的醫師之中，不乏知名的科學家，如施靈（Klaus Karl Schilling）曾是國際瘧疾研究聯盟的成員，戰時卻刻意讓一千多名囚犯感染瘧疾來進行科學研究。科學家在戰爭期間荒唐的行徑，讓美國醫師里昂&middot;亞歷山大（Leo Alexander）動筆起草人體實驗中應有的道德規範，也就是今日我們熟知的「紐倫堡公約」，寫明了醫師在任何情況之下，都不得傷害受試者（除非受試者就是醫師本人）。而1964年在芬蘭舉辦的全球醫師大會更提出「赫爾辛基宣言（The Declaration of Helsinki）」，說明了受試者有絕對的權利了解實驗內容，保障了受試者「知情同意」的權益。數十年的努力之下，美國和其他國家都誓言杜絕非人道的臨床實驗，全世界都認為這種惡魔般的人體實驗不會再出現了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qp60jU2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqp60jU2.png&h=0f218e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=af8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909&amp;oe=5D8A89DA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Daf8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909%26oe%3D5D8A89DA&h=582c6bc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59327e12224bb2aa084aa4bb7a70431fd0f4837c","tid":1227039,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e24d580c118d8b8f9bd846dafdf5dce3388aa6b2","tid":1227039,"uid":39013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:24:32.000Z","msg":"呢排的心理壓力對於有良知的人黎講真係好大<br />\n其他巴絲都係有事要尋求幫助<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:25:25.000Z","msg":"我都係如果唔係聽一聽 903 / RTHK 電台我都捱唔到"},{"pid":"42657a8a637908deaf4b791105704d8ffa9bc965","tid":1227039,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e24d580c118d8b8f9bd846dafdf5dce3388aa6b2","tid":1227039,"uid":39013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:24:32.000Z","msg":"呢排的心理壓力對於有良知的人黎講真係好大<br />\n其他巴絲都係有事要尋求幫助<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:25:33.000Z","msg":"有無連登社工幫下手， 我好抑鬱"},{"pid":"ab667f48cbe9854837ed0f53224e661ce5677d8c","tid":1227039,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:25:58.000Z","msg":"個心好撚痛，咁嘅政府唔值得為佢無左條命"},{"pid":"3542aced8693ef9200745d89e1fe5e0454211f35","tid":1227039,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab667f48cbe9854837ed0f53224e661ce5677d8c","tid":1227039,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:25:58.000Z","msg":"個心好撚痛，咁嘅政府唔值得為佢無左條命"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:29:45.000Z","msg":"我就頂